        "full-negative": {
          "status": "pending",
          "reason": "Mechanical recolor-white fails for Itaú: the brand is a composite block (blue background #1a5493 + yellow wordmark #fff212 layered on top). Recoloring all fills to white collapses both layers into a solid white square, erasing the 'Itaú' wordmark. The current itau-full-negative.svg file on disk is broken output from one such derive run and must NOT be referenced from src/config/payment-instruments.ts. Awaiting either (a) an official negative variant from Itaú brand resources, or (b) a hand-crafted variant that preserves the blue block and recolors only the wordmark to white.",
          "lastEvaluatedAt": "2026-04-27T15:56:58.977Z"
        },
        "mark-positive": {
          "status": "pending",
          "reason": "Itaú uses a unified block lockup (rounded blue square + yellow wordmark) as its complete brand mark — there is no isolatable isotype distinct from the wordmark. The full-positive file already serves both full and compact rendering contexts; payment-instruments.ts can reference itau-full-positive.svg for both `logo` and `compactLogo` fields without quality loss.",
          "lastEvaluatedAt": "2026-04-27T15:56:58.977Z"
        },
